-- MOVES-Pictet hires multi-asset team from Barings Asset Management 
-- By Neha Dimri in Bangalore
-- Mon Nov 17, 2014 08:02AM EST
-- None



Nov 17 (Reuters) - Swiss asset manager Pictet Asset Management hired a team from Barings Asset Management to manage multi-asset funds.

Percival Stanion, Andrew Cole and Shaniel Ramjee built multi-asset strategies at Barings. The team will be led by Stanion, who joins as head of multi-asset strategies (excluding Switzerland), Pictet said.